CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

January 15, 2003

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

1992-2019. State v. Fox.

Wood App. No. 90-WD-067. Original petition for a new sentencing hearing, motion for stay of execution, and request for oral argument. Petition dismissed, motion denied, and request denied.

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Cook, Lundberg Stratton and O’Connor, JJ., concur. Moyer, C. J., and Pfeifer, J., dissent.
